  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/d90895fb8ea75aae9dacd1468e031621.avif?t=1726729031\" width=616 height=282 /></span><br><br>Marble Abduction! is a brand new kind of rolling experience. Hand-crafted levels, intuitive and customizable controls, the highest visual quality and reliable and robust physics make for a truly out-of-this-world marbling experience!<br><br>Inspired by games like Super Monkey Ball, Marble it Up, Mirror's Edge and more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/bec731e465d11087d0604f289caa1c73.poster.avif?t=1726729031\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/bec731e465d11087d0604f289caa1c73.webm?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/bec731e465d11087d0604f289caa1c73.mp4?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>70 unique hand-crafted tracks filled with hazardous obstacles, multiple paths, and sensational powerups, and the mind-blowing visuals!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/f195f137eac5d6c61d247ab8ba7fa4a9.poster.avif?t=1726729031\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/f195f137eac5d6c61d247ab8ba7fa4a9.webm?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/f195f137eac5d6c61d247ab8ba7fa4a9.mp4?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>80 unique marbles ready to be added to your collection. Find hidden collectibles in the tracks and complete challenge runs to unlock rare marbles. Complete tracks in lightning fast speeds to unlock even rarer marbles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/24709dbd4e340b2522e4fe25c5306c97.poster.avif?t=1726729031\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/24709dbd4e340b2522e4fe25c5306c97.webm?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/24709dbd4e340b2522e4fe25c5306c97.mp4?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Compete with yourself and others around the world for coveted spots on the leaderboard. It's a tough challenge but you're up for the task, right?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/0fc2e35717fda77e17e94a3f63c3ec3e.poster.avif?t=1726729031\" width=308 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/0fc2e35717fda77e17e94a3f63c3ec3e.webm?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/d116cd59a7d150b224f4fb3b489c3150.poster.avif?t=1726729031\" width=308 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2440080/extras/d116cd59a7d150b224f4fb3b489c3150.webm?t=1726729031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" a